:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Sept 03, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104zce1665702892792.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/zce1665702892792.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/zce1665702892792.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"zce1665702892792\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      uDdeExecute\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"zce1665702892792__uddeexecute_114167\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Sends a command string to a DDE server application.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"zce1665702892792__topic_d35600e1_d35601e1_d35602e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1218951e53\">Parameters</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"zce1665702892792__table_d3566e1_d3567e1_d3568e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" rowspan=\"3\">\n in:\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" rowspan=\"1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">$50</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" rowspan=\"1\">\n Service name\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" rowspan=\"1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">$51</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" rowspan=\"1\">\n Topic name\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">$53</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n Data item\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n out:\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" rowspan=\"1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$status</span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" rowspan=\"1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">0</code>=success, <code class=\"ph codeph\">-1</code>=failure </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"zce1665702892792__topic_d23252e1_d23253e1_d23254e1_d23255e1_d23256e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1218951e143\">\n                        \n Description\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"zce1665702892792__p_d35609e1_d35610e1_d35611e1\">The syntax and semantics of the command string depend on the server application.</p>\n<div class=\"note note note_note\" id=\"zce1665702892792__note_w5811ab1b5b5b5_w5812ab1b5b5_w5813ab1b5_w5814ab1\"><span class=\"note__title\">Note:</span> The maximum number of bytes sent by uDdeExecute is set by UGETREGC. Currently, this is 7999 bytes.</div>\n<div class=\"div\">\n<p class=\"p\">In the following example, <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">uDdeExecute</span> is used to open a worksheet in OpenOffice Calc, move the focus to a certain cell and paste the contents of a Uniface field into that cell:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">$50=\"Calc\"\n$51=\"system\"\n$53=\"[Open(%%\"c:/wrksht.ods%%\")][Select(%%\"R4C5%%\")][Formula(%%\"%%field%%%%%\")]\"\nactivate \"udde\".uDdeExecute()\nif ($status=0)\n message \"Execute succeeded\"\nelse\n message \"Execute did not succeed\"\nendif\n</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2534386\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2534386\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "uDdeExecute Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Sept 03, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 uDdeExecute Sends a command string to a DDE server application. Parameters in: $50 Service name $51 Topic name $53 Data item out: $status 0 =success, -1 =failure Description The syntax and semantics of the command string depend on the server application. Note: The maximum number of bytes sent by uDdeExecute is set by UGETREGC. Currently, this is 7999 bytes. In the following example, uDdeExecute is used to open a worksheet in OpenOffice Calc, move the focus to a certain cell and paste the contents of a Uniface field into that cell: $50=\"Calc\" $51=\"system\" $53=\"[Open(%%\"c:/wrksht.ods%%\")][Select(%%\"R4C5%%\")][Formula(%%\"%%field%%%%%\")]\" activate \"udde\".uDdeExecute() if ($status=0) message \"Execute succeeded\" else message \"Execute did not succeed\" endif Copy Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}